<br>
Yes it is unfortunate that you can not enter the zones with all of your friends. But do you really want the lower level members of the party spending 90 minutes putting their armor back on? Or the higher level members /yawning at the MOBs throughout the adventure? I know I don’t.<br>
<br>
Personally, I have no intention of entering an LDoN zone with anyone below level 60 and I would prefer that everyone be 65.  I want the best that the zone can throw at me and I want to have my best chance at beating it.<br>
<br>
Ice<br>
